I think the problem is too complex for a CoC.
Also with your given limit on x it can be solved in python with brute force:

equation = input().split('=')
for x in range(-100, 101):
    try:
        if eval(equation[0].replace('x',str(x))) == eval(equation[1].replace('x',str(x))):
            print(x)
    except:
        pass

a=input().replace('=','==')
for x in range(-100,101):
    if eval(a):print(x)

